#. type: Title =
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/grpc-service-implementation.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Reflection Service"
msgstr "Serviço de Reflexão"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/grpc-service-implementation.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus gRPC Server implements the https://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/master/doc/server-reflection.md[reflection service].\n"
"This service allows tools like https://github.com/fullstorydev/grpcurl[grpcurl] or https://github.com/gusaul/grpcox[grpcox] to interact with your services."
msgstr "O servidor gRPC do Quarkus implementa o link:https://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/master/doc/server-reflection.md[serviço de reflexão] . Esse serviço permite que ferramentas como link:https://github.com/fullstorydev/grpcurl[o grpcurl] ou link:https://github.com/gusaul/grpcox[o grpcox] interajam com seus serviços."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/grpc-service-implementation.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"The reflection service is enabled by default in _dev_ mode.\n"
"In test or production mode, you need to enable it explicitly by setting `quarkus.grpc.server.enable-reflection-service` to `true`."
msgstr "O serviço de reflexão está habilitado por padrão no modo _de desenvolvimento_ . Nos modos de teste ou produção, é necessário habilitá-lo explicitamente, definindo `quarkus.grpc.server.enable-reflection-service` como `true` ."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/grpc-service-implementation.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Quarkus exposes both the reflection service `v1` and `v1alpha`."
msgstr "O Quarkus disponibiliza tanto o serviço de reflexão `v1` quanto `o v1alpha` ."

#. type: Title =
